      "source": [
        "# AraBERT Fine-Tuning for Arabic Dialect Sentiment Classification\n",
        "**Model:** `aubmindlab/bert-base-arabertv02`  \n",
        "**Task:** Binary Sentiment Classification (positive / negative)  \n",
        "**Framework:** PyTorch + HuggingFace Transformers  \n",
        "**Strategy:** Staged fine-tuning with layer freezing"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "1NtMuJ7Ofynx"
      },
      "source": [
        "## Cell 1 — Install & Import Dependencies"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 28,
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "5GRQQ1cdfyny",
        "outputId": "e2b747cc-0a55-4128-ca2e-0fd3157f34a5"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
